    <text>
        <body>
            <div frus:doc-dateTime-max="1934-06-30T11:00:00-05:00"
                frus:doc-dateTime-min="1934-06-30T11:00:00-05:00" n="194"
                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d194">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">862.00/3283: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The Ambassador in Germany</hi> (<persName type="from">
                        <hi rend="italic">Dodd</hi>
                    </persName>) <hi rend="italic">to the <gloss type="to">Secretary of
                            State</gloss>
                    </hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Berlin</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1934-06-30T17:00:00+01:00"
                            >June 30, 1934—5 p.m.</date>
                        <lb/>[Received June 30—1:55 p.m.]</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>124. Some outbreaks of unruly elements were made in Munich yesterday. Last night
                    Hitler arrived after conference with Goering at the Krupp works took charge of
                    the S.A. forces and reestablished order. Today at 1 o’clock Goering took charge
                    of the S.A. offices in Berlin which had been under the direction of the
                    recalcitrant Roehm. Several arrests were made and a few S.A. officials committed
                    suicide and former Chancellor Schleicher has been killed. Reports indicate that
                    movements have been made in other cities. Proclamation from Hitler calling on
                    all S.A. troops to give perfect obedience to the new commander Lutze has been
                    issued. “With complete obedience and submitting to perfect discipline you must
                    help us create and develop the new German race.”</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Dodd</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
